erators had become entrenched in what few Twine tutorials existed at the ti=
me, including Anna Anthropy&#39;s). Furthermore, due to the use of doubled =
brackets, nesting macros inside each other was out of the question: designi=
ng a custom macro for nesting, like <code><span class=3D"cm-harlowe-2-inequ=
ality cm-harlowe-2-root">&lt;</span><span class=3D"cm-harlowe-2-inequality =
cm-harlowe-2-root">&lt;</span><span class=3D"cm-harlowe-2-text cm-harlowe-2=
